  "description": "Seed taxonomy package manifest for China mainland and Taiwan biodiversity survey modules. This manifest records package metadata and expected capabilities; it is not an exhaustive species list. Terrestrial vertebrate packages reference a shared representative seed asset, while plant and insect packages now ship real minimal seed assets for importer validation and offline lookup wiring.",
